Program: Discovery
Title: The coffee trade
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwtm
Last Broadcast Date: 17 February 1997
Report on coffee, its trade, health implications and history. A special report from Seattle, US the city where coffee is taken very seriously. The city also happens to be hosting an international science event. Medical professionals are not united on whether coffee is good or bad for us.